{
  "id": "6622862c0fdfb80024de5dcd",
  "title": "研修中バッジをつけた店員さんの練習台になる",
  "created": 1713538606,
  "updated": 1718006220,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6622862c0fdfb80024de5dcd",
      "text": "研修中バッジをつけた店員さんの練習台になる",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713538606,
      "updated": 1713538606
    },
    {
      "id": "6622862eb759d700008c3ab9",
      "text": "[yuyuko.icon]なんとなく意識していること",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713538606,
      "updated": 1713538616
    },
    {
      "id": "66228630b759d700008c3aba",
      "text": " 笑顔でいる",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713538609,
      "updated": 1713538732
    },
    {
      "id": "66228650b759d700008c3abc",
      "text": " なにか手間取っているっぽいときは、スマホを見るなどして視線をそらす",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713538640,
      "updated": 1713538671
    },
    {
      "id": "66228671b759d700008c3abd",
      "text": " 「急がないので[大丈夫]です」を意識的に言う",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713538674,
      "updated": 1713538742
    },
    {
      "id": "66228724b759d700008c3abe",
      "text": " 用件が済んだら、はっきりお礼を言う",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713538852,
      "updated": 1713538883
    },
    {
      "id": "662287aab759d700008c3abf",
      "text": "  ヘルプに来た先輩（と思われる人）にだけお礼して済ませない。研修中の本人にも顔を向けて言う",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713538986,
      "updated": 1713539167
    },
    {
      "id": "66228714be12ad0000f5b328",
      "text": " [2024/04/19#66223466b759d7000062839e]",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713538836,
      "updated": 1713601542
    },
    {
      "id": "66237c07b759d70000a5b709",
      "text": "  善良なチュートリアル要員に徹する",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713601543,
      "updated": 1713601551
    },
    {
      "id": "66237c0fb759d70000a5b70a",
      "text": "  \t[マック]で[株主優待券]を出すと研修生が「なんだこれ？」という顔してチーフを呼び出す姿がよく見られ、大人しく待って焦らせないようにしている[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713601552,
      "updated": 1713601562
    },
    {
      "id": "66237c20b759d70000a5b70b",
      "text": "  本当は「頑張ってくださいね〜」とか話しかけたいけど、マニュアルにないことを言って流れを乱したくないので我慢してる",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713601570,
      "updated": 1713601570
    },
    {
      "id": "66237bf8b759d70000a5b708",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b10baafcc4e900014b759d7",
      "created": 1713601528,
      "updated": 1713601528
    },
    {
      "id": "66228719be12ad0000f5b329",
      "text": "[sume.icon]",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1713538842,
      "updated": 1713538877
    },
    {
      "id": "66228720be12ad0000f5b32a",
      "text": "　バーコード向けて並べる",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1713538848,
      "updated": 1713538856
    },
    {
      "id": "6623063a79d3a90000e07fc8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1713571388,
      "updated": 1713571388
    },
    {
      "id": "6623063a79d3a90000e07fc9",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1713571388,
      "updated": 1713571388
    },
    {
      "id": "6623063b79d3a90000e07fcb",
      "text": "\t無言で辛抱強く待つ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1713571389,
      "updated": 1713571395
    },
    {
      "id": "6623065e79d3a90000e07fcd",
      "text": "\t\tじっと見ると威圧的になるので、鳥みたいにあらぬ方向を向いて待つ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1713571424,
      "updated": 1713571441
    },
    {
      "id": "6623064179d3a90000e07fcc",
      "text": "\t喋るのは苦手だが会釈は多めに出して非言語で「大丈夫ですよ」感を伝える",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1713571395,
      "updated": 1713571413
    },
    {
      "id": "6623063b79d3a90000e07fca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1713571388,
      "updated": 1713571388
    },
    {
      "id": "6666b126c3f2c700003b5b69",
      "text": "[maichan.icon]",
      "userId": "615026d6d6a2280023c3f2c7",
      "created": 1718006054,
      "updated": 1718006056
    },
    {
      "id": "6666b128c3f2c700003b5b6b",
      "text": "　お願いしますとかありがとうとか気持ち大きな声ではっきり言う",
      "userId": "615026d6d6a2280023c3f2c7",
      "created": 1718006057,
      "updated": 1718006123
    },
    {
      "id": "6666b18fc3f2c700003b5b6c",
      "text": "　この仕事をしてよかったなぁと思われるようなお客さんになれたらいいなぁ",
      "userId": "615026d6d6a2280023c3f2c7",
      "created": 1718006160,
      "updated": 1718006220
    },
    {
      "id": "6666b127c3f2c700003b5b6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "615026d6d6a2280023c3f2c7",
      "created": 1718006056,
      "updated": 1718006056
    }
  ]
}